textContent: Setup your way to home cinema
Extremely easy to setup and use!

contentList.title: What do you need?
contentList.description: You will need a mobile phone or a functional computer and a projector to project the image on your wall.

contentList.title: How it works?
contentList.description: You set up whatever you want to project on your wall in your computer or mobile phone and use appropriate software for that.

contentList.title: Data & resources consumtion
contentList.description: Depends on the nature of your content it can be quite consuming when it comes to data and resources. but there is a room for optimization to reduce the size and make it more consumtion-friendly.
